### Cross-service Kafka demo
### 1) Create master_data through Kong as ACCOUNTANT.
### 2) Open Kafka UI topic master-data-events.
### 3) Read audit events through Kong.

### Create master_data through Kong
POST http://localhost:18000/api/master-data
Authorization: Bearer <ACCOUNTANT_ACCESS_TOKEN>
Content-Type: application/json
X-Request-Id: cross-service-create-001

{
  "code": "KAFKA-DEMO-{{$timestamp}}",
  "name": "Kafka cross-service demo item",
  "category": "Demo",
  "isActive": true
}

### Read audit events through Kong
GET http://localhost:18000/api/audit-events?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer <ACCOUNTANT_ACCESS_TOKEN>
X-Request-Id: cross-service-audit-001

### Missing token should remain blocked
GET http://localhost:18000/api/audit-events
X-Request-Id: cross-service-audit-missing-token
